  <data key="d1">"龚光杰 is a martial arts master who fights段誉 and is frustrated by his inability to dodge his palm strike."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"龚光杰 is a warrior engaged in a fierce battle against an unknown intelligence, showcasing his determination and the chaotic environment of the fight."&lt;SEP&gt;"龚光杰 is another disciple of the无量剑, involved in the confrontation with the神农帮."&lt;SEP&gt;"龚光杰是神农帮的弟子，参与与未知智能的沟通，表现出紧张和警惕的神情。"</data>
