  <data key="d1">"左子穆 is a character who challenges段誉 and wants to teach him martial arts."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"左子穆 is a martial artist involved in a critical confrontation, demonstrating his skill and the tension of the situation."&lt;SEP&gt;"左子穆 is the master, involved in the conflict with the神农帮."&lt;SEP&gt;"左子穆是神农帮的成员，负责监控信件并阻止龚光杰接触，其言行透露出对未知力量的警惕。"</data>
