<node id="&quot;无量剑&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"无量剑 is an organization involved in the conflict, representing the forces at play in the battle against the unknown intelligence."&lt;SEP&gt;"无量剑是与神农帮有恩怨的敌对组织，段誉因目睹其成员惨死而欲劝解。&gt;"&lt;SEP&gt;"无量剑是神农帮的分支，擅长武艺但缺乏毒术，其成员在战斗中被击败，凸显其弱点。"</data>
