<node id="&quot;干光豪&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"干光豪 is a disciple of the无量剑, involved in the confrontation with the神农帮."&lt;SEP&gt;"干光豪是东宗西宗的掌门，与葛师妹共同经历剑湖事件，展现家族纽带。"&lt;SEP&gt;"干光豪是段誉的对手，与葛师妹成婚，意图阻止段誉与未知智能体的接触，展现传统宗门的势力。"</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-08862469dfa54cb6af7b0752018bf315&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd997cbcd5a121e3e43d73fa6084fbac&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-73e81947ba085538dfb2fd722b3f065f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;神农帮&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A secret society in the novel, known for its violent practices and involvement in the story's conflicts."&lt;SEP&gt;"神农帮 is an organization that is mentioned in the text as the one who captured "钟灵"."&lt;SEP&gt;"神农帮是主要的组织，钟灵等人隶属于此帮，致力于采药制药，但因闪电貂的威胁而面临挑战。"&lt;SEP&gt;"神农帮是故事中的主要组织，与钟灵、司空玄存在冲突，涉及生死符等神秘力量。"&lt;SEP&gt;"神农帮是段誉所属的帮派，与无量剑有矛盾，段誉试图化解双方恩怨。&gt;"&lt;SEP&gt;"神农帮是虚构的组织，掌握着与未知智能沟通的权限，其行动威胁到武林的平衡。"</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-067c9ef037d04fbaa1e846b53f8153ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b81acad343b1b6f6f02c7f1f9430d03&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e050a28ccd170106cbe5386fddea1d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8afc427c4cc929f6a6e369a8d408596d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4512cfc06d43cc28ac2d1c323ab9487b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4e05afb7d44a061e7b569b28b32db7ed</data>
