<node id="&quot;FIRST CONTACT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"First Contact is the initial communication between Duan Yu's team and the unknown intelligence, marking a pivotal moment in their journey."&lt;SEP&gt;"First Contact is the pivotal event where Zhan Zilong encounters the unknown intelligence and attempts to communicate through the Resonant Chessboard, marking a critical turning point in the story."&lt;SEP&gt;"First Contact is the potential initial communication between humanity and an unknown intelligence, a pivotal event in the narrative that tests the protagonists' resolve and adaptability."&lt;SEP&gt;"First Contact is the potential initial communication between humanity and an unknown intelligence."&lt;SEP&gt;"First Contact是段誉与未知智能体的首次接触，涉及解药和通信。"&lt;SEP&gt;"First Contact是段誉和钟万仇之间的重要事件，涉及首次接触未知智能体。"&lt;SEP&gt;"First Contact是段誉团队与未知智能体的首次接触，他们需要去大理。"&lt;SEP&gt;"The potential initial communication between humanity and an unknown intelligence."&lt;SEP&gt;"段誉与黑衣女郎的冲突可视为首次接触的事件，涉及人类与未知智能的互动。"</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ba2222d48105cae142ebbd362ed41cc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7042d44b19adbb4a1e427845c77603c5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f2f867906a687ef5b12ded952687685&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1cee534b89bc93c9ae26e26feb6e2d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7d52f2751f82971bd2856d671d95ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c50011b20c2ee043f8f12d02d25cf938&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e050a28ccd170106cbe5386fddea1d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4201f5703017f87fd8ab36135f67ed5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-923dcd068bac0210535287573cdcafd0</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HUMANITY'S RESPONSE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Humanity's Response is the collective action taken by Zan Yu's team to address a message from the unknown intelligence, reflecting their transformation from passive observers to active participants."&lt;SEP&gt;"Humanity's Response refers to the collective action taken by Duan Yu's team to engage with the unknown intelligence, reflecting their determination to understand and interact with the cosmic message."&lt;SEP&gt;"Humanity's Response是团队应对未知智能体的行动，包含解药和通信策略。"&lt;SEP&gt;"Humanity's Response是段誉团队对未知智能体的回应，他们需要去大理。"&lt;SEP&gt;"The collective action taken by段誉's team in response to a message from an unknown intelligence."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-ba2222d48105cae142ebbd362ed41cc9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1cee534b89bc93c9ae26e26feb6e2d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d7d52f2751f82971bd2856d671d95ae4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d4201f5703017f87fd8ab36135f67ed5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-923dcd068bac0210535287573cdcafd0</data>
</node>
